OL,3,CWhy are thousands of prisoners to be
OL,4,Creleased early from UK jails?
OL,6,FBut how will the measures work, and
OL,7,Fhow much risk do they pose?
OL,9,FWhat is the plan?
OL,11,FTo free up space in prisons, the
OL,12,Fgovernment announced in July that some
OL,13,Fprisoners would be released after
OL,14,Fserving only 40% of their sentence
OL,15,Frather than 50% - as required under
OL,16,Fprevious guidelines.
OL,18,FThe first set of prisoners to be
OL,19,Freleased from the September 10 are
OL,20,Fthose who were given sentences of five
OL,21,Fyears or less.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
