OL,3,CWhy are thousands of prisoners to be
OL,4,Creleased early from UK jails?
OL,6,FThere are exceptions, however. Those
OL,7,Fserving sentences for sex and violent
OL,8,Foffences are excluded, as are some
OL,9,Foffences related to domestic violence.
OL,11,FA total of 5,500 prisoners are
OL,12,Fexpected to be let out, along with a
OL,13,Fsecond release from October of those
OL,14,Fserving five years or more.
OL,16,FAre there risks?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
