OL,11,FWhy have prisons become full?
OL,13,FExperts say a combination of longer
OL,14,Fsentences for crimes, the creation of
OL,15,Fnew offences, record numbers of
OL,16,Freleased prisoners being recalled, and
OL,17,FCovid court backlogs have all
OL,18,Fcontributed.
